---
title: The Works Beef & Beetroot Relish Burger with Fries, Fried Egg & Garlic Aioli
description: Team burger is off to a smashing start! Straight out of the gate with a cheesy beef pattie, followed up by the all-star combo of a sweet beetroot relish and fried egg. Drive it home with the winning move: serving up this delicious burger with a side of fries. Game, set and match!
